{"tid":881163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國父子昆士蘭游泳溺斃","createTime":"2018-10-29T08:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T00:47:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7db778c80c280004d303e6d067fda6d1f2afc009","tid":881163,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T08:32:39.000Z","msg":"一對中國父子在澳洲昆士蘭游泳時不幸遇溺身亡。外國傳媒指該對父子為遊客，父子分別是30歲和5歲。<br />\n<br />\n事發於當地時間周日（28日）下午，一名30歲中國男子與其5歲兒子在昆士蘭北部旅遊熱點艾爾利海灘潟湖（Airlie Beach Lagoon）游泳時不幸遇溺。二人獲救時已失去意識，心臟驟停，情況危急。救護人員下午4時左右趕到現場，將他們送至附近的普拉瑟潘醫院（Proserpine Hospital），經搶救後不治。<br />\n<br />\n當時正在潟湖附近的一名女士稱，沒有發現任何異常情況，沒有聽到喊叫聲，直到看完手中的書，才發現潟湖岸邊有一輛救護車，並有兩人正接受心肺復蘇急救。其他目擊者表示，他們曾看到成年男子在橋下游泳，而男孩則跳入水中。據悉，事發當日氣溫高達35度，湖裏有數百人游泳，很多都是兒童。<br />\n<br />\n(悉尼先驅晨報/澳洲第九新聞/海外網)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181029/s00004/1540776760699\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181029%2Fs00004%2F1540776760699&d=7329xsprZlMi8AYOta0tnBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=7affc938\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181029%2Fs00004%2F1540776760699&h=d900ac0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181029/s00004/1540776760699</a>"},{"pid":"0c4ae0982f7a15a4f0cee9f023694a4e53363ed5","tid":881163,"uid":156652,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T08:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSFvMss.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSFvMss.gif&h=9fba544e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e41c9ad61e09c9f850535f819a4cd4b055780a83","tid":881163,"uid":4574,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T08:58:06.000Z","msg":"污染海洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467c6d9e326d5730241eaa4f86fa12d919604fe0","tid":881163,"uid":211579,"like":